@startuml
title Data Flow - Lead Qualification

actor SalesRep
participant Gateway
participant LeadService
participant AIService
queue Kafka
participant NotificationService

SalesRep -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/leads
Gateway -> LeadService: Create lead
LeadService -> Kafka: LeadCreatedEvent
Kafka -> AIService: Score lead
AIService -> Kafka: LeadScoredEvent
Kafka -> NotificationService: Notify rep
@enduml
